@wp.kernel

    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos((v0 + v2))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.38)))
    v1 = wp.abs(0.79)
    v0 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.86) - (v0 + 0.56 / tmp + 0.08)) / wp.abs((v2 + 0.49 / v0 + 0.89)))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs(0.23))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.07)))
    data[tid] = v0
